Please provide input on the name of the System property that enables the feature. I'd like to then rename the class to match the property if possible.

You need to run `gradlew spotlessApply` to fix formatting.

I like the idea to make it easier to deploy extensions to the core product.  This change automatically updates the classpath for gfsh (making it easier to use custom commands) and the locator/server (so you don't have to manually specify jars on the command line).

@upthewaterspout I don't see any security concerns, do you?

